overview: DOGMAN! He is a highly experienced hero who guards the streets. After losing everything he loves and has fought for since he was a teenager, he faces Charly, who will reveal himself as his creator and reality and fiction no longer have a dividing line. Faced with the loss of his own identity, DOGMAN! he will try to prevail over Charly, a strange being, who seems to be able to control everything, except his own destiny.

production_companies.name: Instituto Superior de Cine y Artes Audiovisuales de Santa Fe
